10:20.344 --> 10:24.172
My new bent outlook
has completely reenergized me.

10:24.240 --> 10:29.033
I'm even dating a young
Brazilian retired actress.[ All Congratulating ]

10:29.102 --> 10:31.447
Some say I'm
robbing the cradle,

10:31.517 --> 10:34.447
but I say she's
robbing the grave.

10:34.517 --> 10:37.033
Howdy, doodies!
What's new?

10:40.033 --> 10:42.965
I was just regaling
your former coworkers...

10:43.033 --> 10:45.861
with a tale of bedroom antics
the likes of which--

10:45.931 --> 10:47.931
Yeah, yeah, big whoop.
No one cares.

10:48.000 --> 10:51.172
I got Bender-related news.
I'm in love.

10:51.240 --> 10:53.654
And I'm takin' all my friends
out to celebrate.

10:53.724 --> 10:56.793
[ All Cheering ][ Amy ]
Let's go live it up!

10:56.861 --> 10:58.931
[ Groans ]

11:01.586 --> 11:05.654
Hey, look at this crowd.
You guys gotta try the pasta.

11:05.724 --> 11:08.240
It's got a real nice
profit margin.

11:08.309 --> 11:10.447
Bam! So, special
occasion tonight?

11:10.517 --> 11:13.413
Oh, Elzar, you'll never
guess what's happened!

11:13.481 --> 11:16.793
- Bam?
- I've met the most
dynamite ladybot.

11:16.861 --> 11:18.826
Hey, that's terrific.

11:18.895 --> 11:23.413
To celebrate, I'm gonna stick
seven copies of my latest
cookbook on your bill.

11:23.481 --> 11:25.274
Bless you, sir.

11:25.344 --> 11:29.206
So, Bender, tell us about
this new girlfriend of yours.

11:29.274 --> 11:33.033
I intend to, through
the lost art of the toast.

11:33.102 --> 11:36.033
To Angleene!
She's got it all--

11:36.102 --> 11:40.274
looks, charm and the love
of a fabulous bending robot.

11:40.344 --> 11:42.481
She sure does.

11:44.309 --> 11:47.240
[ Both Giggling ]

11:47.309 --> 11:50.481
Flexo!
[ Grunting ]

11:52.240 --> 11:54.724
Careful!
That's a week old!

12:02.206 --> 12:06.586
I finally meet a nice girl,
with a pair of legs
that don't quit unexpectedly,

12:06.654 --> 12:09.724
and that jerk Flexo
steals her away?

12:09.793 --> 12:13.240
It's time to kick
some shiny metal ass!

12:13.309 --> 12:16.033
You degenerate hussy!

12:16.102 --> 12:18.344
I'm disappointed
in you too, Angleene.

12:18.413 --> 12:20.724
Bender, it's-it's
not what you think.

12:20.793 --> 12:23.481
Oh, God, then it's worse
than I think!

12:23.551 --> 12:26.688
Now look, there is
no reason to be upset.

12:26.758 --> 12:29.965
- Flexo and I are divorced.
- Div-- Huh?

12:30.033 --> 12:32.620
We're just havin' dinner
'cause we wanna stay friends.

12:32.688 --> 12:34.654
Ah, I knew that.

12:34.724 --> 12:38.033
What I'm actually outraged by
is your choice of wine!

12:38.102 --> 12:40.517
Really,
it's the steward's fault.[ Slap ]

12:40.586 --> 12:42.481
Excellent choice, sir.

12:44.206 --> 12:47.309
That Flexo!
Why, I'm knockin' him
right on his butt.

12:47.379 --> 12:49.309
Can't believe this.
[ Muttering ]

12:49.379 --> 12:51.379
Obsessing won't help, Bender.

12:51.447 --> 12:54.067
Take a lean back
and enjoy life.

12:54.136 --> 12:57.724
I can't. My fembot may be
in love with another manbot.

12:57.793 --> 13:02.136
Well, talk to her.
Tell her about your feelings
in an open and honest way.

13:02.206 --> 13:04.240
Yeah. Either that
or be a man.

13:04.309 --> 13:07.551
[ Bender ] Okay, I've constructed an elaborate lie.

13:07.620 --> 13:11.067
I'll call Angleene
while pretending to be Flexo,

13:11.136 --> 13:13.481
arrange a date,
show up disguised as him...

13:13.551 --> 13:15.861
and catch her
two-timing me with myself.

13:15.931 --> 13:18.586
That's thinkin' like a man.

13:18.654 --> 13:21.000
♪♪ [ Touch Tones ]

13:21.067 --> 13:24.654
Hello? This is Flexo.

13:29.309 --> 13:31.274
[ Door Opens, Closes ]

13:34.654 --> 13:39.517
Now we'll see who loves whom.
[ Sinister Laughing ]

13:39.586 --> 13:43.965
♪♪ [ Rock ][ Chattering ]

13:46.688 --> 13:49.895
Hey, hot stuff.Hey, Flexo.

13:49.965 --> 13:53.551
So since when do you go
to bars on work nights?

13:53.620 --> 13:57.447
