It's exactly like me.

13:57.517 --> 14:02.413
Flexo, the fun-lovin' love
machine fembots love to love.

14:02.481 --> 14:04.793
Hey, barkeep,
I'll have a fuzzy navel,

14:04.861 --> 14:07.344
and she'll have
the girliest drink in the house.

14:07.413 --> 14:09.206
Two fuzzy navels comin' up.

14:09.274 --> 14:12.206
I hope they can make
change for a fortune.

14:12.274 --> 14:16.965
Yo, get an eyeload of that
filthy scab with the beard...

14:17.033 --> 14:19.309
flashin' his filthy
scab money.

14:19.379 --> 14:21.861
- It's an insult to you, boss.
- Yeah.

14:21.931 --> 14:25.344
That cash oughta be slushin'
my fund and kicks-in' my back.

14:25.413 --> 14:27.379
I'm greasin' up my whoozits.

14:27.447 --> 14:29.413
Whoa, whoa, Clamps.
Not yet.

14:29.481 --> 14:32.931
Let's just keep an eye on him
and see if he does it
a couple more times.

14:33.000 --> 14:35.551
You're looking good
to Flexo tonight.

14:35.620 --> 14:38.793
Quit makin'
with the googly eyes. You know
that I'm in love with Bender.

14:38.861 --> 14:41.379
Bender?
That walkin' wuss factory?

14:41.447 --> 14:45.413
He may be a walkin' factory,
but believe me, he is no wuss.

14:45.481 --> 14:48.895
Now look, you and me
are through. I told you that
when I divorced you.

14:48.965 --> 14:51.240
But goin' through
a divorce together,

14:51.309 --> 14:53.517
you can't tell me that
didn't bring us closer.

14:53.586 --> 14:55.067
Care to dance?

14:55.136 --> 14:58.240
Well, you know
I love dancin', but
you always hated it.

14:58.309 --> 15:02.895
In that case,
it's somethin' I've always
wanted to make up to you.

15:02.965 --> 15:06.206
♪♪ [ Techno ]

15:07.965 --> 15:09.931
Hey, Scratchmo!

15:10.000 --> 15:13.309
How about droppin'
me and the lady
some rump-rattlin' beats?

15:13.379 --> 15:15.895
I had hoped by the second time
he flashed his cash,

15:15.965 --> 15:17.895
my rage would've subsided.

15:17.965 --> 15:20.413
Sadly, that
has not happened.

15:21.931 --> 15:24.344
♪♪ [ Techno Continues ]

15:24.413 --> 15:27.309
You used to be
so inflexible, Flexo.

15:27.379 --> 15:29.309
You have really
loosened up.

15:29.379 --> 15:31.826
I recently upgraded
my funk card.

15:31.895 --> 15:34.172
[ Grunting ]
Come on!

15:34.240 --> 15:36.965
All right!Come on, now!

15:37.033 --> 15:39.481
What's new? Huh?

15:44.688 --> 15:47.309
Ugh!

15:47.379 --> 15:49.654
Flexo?
What's goin' on?

15:49.724 --> 15:52.654
[ Laughs ]
Did, um--

15:52.724 --> 15:55.688
Oh! Flexo!

15:55.758 --> 15:59.240
[ All Shouting ]

16:07.067 --> 16:09.654
So the moral of the story is...

16:09.724 --> 16:12.724
if you want it to stay sunk,
tie a weight to it!

16:12.793 --> 16:15.447
[ Both Laughing ]

16:15.517 --> 16:18.379
You know, you always were
a kick in the teeth, man.

16:18.447 --> 16:22.758
Ah, shucks, thunder buns.
You make me feel like
a million volts.

16:22.826 --> 16:25.793
Oh, Flexo, Flexo, Flexo.

16:25.861 --> 16:28.965
I'm startin' to remember
why I fell for you
in the first place.

16:29.033 --> 16:32.895
[ Thinking ]
So, she's fallin' for Flexo, eh?

16:32.965 --> 16:36.413
I'd better seduce her
a little more, just to be sure.

16:36.481 --> 16:39.965
Well, it's late.
I should get home to my trailer.

16:40.033 --> 16:42.000
I'll walk you out.

16:42.067 --> 16:45.481
After all, a true gentlemen
tends to his date's every need.

16:45.551 --> 16:47.481
Tiparillo?

16:50.447 --> 16:52.447
Here you are, my lad.

16:52.517 --> 16:56.793
Bring the lady's car around
in the finest way possible.

16:56.861 --> 16:59.240
He's flashin'
his cash loaf again.

16:59.309 --> 17:02.481
How many times is that?
Two or three?Three.

17:02.551 --> 17:05.689
All right. That's
the necessary number of times.

17:05.758 --> 17:09.309
That scab's gonna have a little
on-the-job accident.

17:09.378 --> 17:11.517
With all due respect,
Donbot,

17:11.586 --> 17:14.275
I don't think we should rely
on an accident happenin'.

17:14.344 --> 17:16.862
- Let's kill him ourselves.
- [ Groans ]

17:16.931 --> 17:20.862
Well, good night.
I had a great time.

17:20.931 --> 17:23.895
How about a lift...
to your place?

17:23.964 --> 17:25.895
- What?
- Admit it.

17:25.964 --> 17:28.240
You felt somethin'
for me tonight.

17:28.309 --> 17:30.481
And by "me"
I mean Flexo.

17:30.550 --> 17:32.448
Hey, look,
I had fun, but--

17:32.517 --> 17:34.448
But?But--

17:34.517 --> 17:38.067
Bu-u-u-t?

17:38.136 --> 17:42.172
[ Panting ]
But--

17:42.240 --> 17:45.448
[ Both Moaning ]

17:50.758 --> 17:54.172
Huh? Bender!
You tricked me!

17:54.240 --> 17:58.067
That's right, baby!
I ain't your
lover boy Flexo,

17:58.136 --> 18:00.067
the guy you love so much!

18:00.136 --> 18:03.103
You even love anybody
pretending to be him!

18:03.172 --> 18:07.309
Well, maybe I love you so much,
I love you no matter who you'repretending to be.

18:07.378 --> 18:11.034
Oh, how I wish I could
believe or understand that!

18:11.103 --> 18:13.792
There's only one reasonable
course of action now.

18:13.862 --> 18:16.792
Kill Flexo! Ow!

18:16.862 --> 18:20.413
No-o-o-o!

18:22.689 --> 18:26.550
♪♪ [ Humming ]

18:28.309 --> 18:31.448
- [ Grunts ]
- Thanks. I appreciate that.

18:31.517 --> 18:34.448
[ Laughs ]
Nah, I'm joshin' ya.
That was quite annoying.

18:34.517 --> 18:36.448
You call yourself divorced?

18:36.517 --> 18:39.205
You're makin' a mockery of one
of our oldest institutions!

18:39.275 --> 18:42.931
What?[ Both Grunting ]

18:44.619 --> 18:47.000
All right, boss.
Give the word,

18:47.067 --> 18:50.275
and I'll drop
this unbendable girder--
clamp, clamp, ka-bamp!

18:50.344 --> 18:53.448
Remember, only kill
the one with the beard.

18:53.517 --> 18:55.964
That other filthy scab,
we got nothin' against.

18:59.034 --> 19:02.000
[ Grunting Continues ]

19:05.758 --> 19:10.172
- That's low!
- Please stop! I'm not worth it!

19:10.240 --> 19:12.689
Probably not,
but I love you,

19:12.758 --> 19:15.619
and I'm gonna kick his ass
till I win you back!

19:15.689 --> 19:18.964
[ Grunting Continues ]

19:19.034 --> 19:23.103
Whoa! Hey! [ Donbot ] Okay, Clamps, now.

19:23.172 --> 19:26.517
- [ Grunts ]
- [ Screaming ]

19:26.586 --> 19:28.826
Oh, that's gotta clamp!

19:30.619 --> 19:32.654
Flexo, are-are you okay?

19:32.723 --> 19:36.275
Yeah. Never better.
[ Coughing ]

19:36.344 --> 19:38.826
Nah, I'm yankin' your chain.
I'm dyin'.

19:38.895 --> 19:42.964
You can't die!
Tonight Bender showed me
that I love you.

19:43.034 --> 19:45.378
But... I love you.

19:45.448 --> 19:48.344
[ Angleene ] I know, and I care for you too.

19:48.413 --> 19:53.862
But I could never love anyone
as much as you made me realize
I love Flexo!

19:53.931 --> 19:57.862
[ Sobbing ]But-- But--

19:57.931 --> 20:01.654
[ Sighs ]
I love you so much,
Angleene,

20:01.723 --> 20:04.309
I want you to be happy,
no matter what.

20:04.378 --> 20:06.481
But what are you sayin'?

20:06.550 --> 20:12.034
I'm sayin' I've got
an unbendable girder to bend.

20:12.103 --> 20:15.000
You can't bend that girder.
It's unbendable!

20:15.067 --> 20:17.586
Well, I don't know
anything about lifting,

20:17.654 --> 20:20.172
so that just leaves us
the one option.

20:20.240 --> 20:23.758
[ Grunting ]

20:35.689 --> 20:38.413
[ Grunting Continues ]

20:45.448 --> 20:49.240
Thanks, buddy.
Another year under that,
and I'd have been a goner.

20:49.309 --> 20:53.034
I'll always
remember this, Bender.

20:54.481 --> 20:57.378
Me too. Me too.

20:57.448 --> 20:59.448
Jerk.

21:02.136 --> 21:06.309
So, Flexo and Angleene
had sex right there
on the factory floor?

21:06.378 --> 21:08.895
Well, at least you got
bending out of your system.

21:08.964 --> 21:14.205
Yes. I won't be up to bending
again for a long, long time.

21:14.275 --> 21:17.378
Perhaps it's your outlook
that needs a good bend--

21:17.448 --> 21:19.378
a 90-degree bend--

21:19.448 --> 21:22.895
to a place where happiness
is perpendicular to wonderment.

21:22.964 --> 21:26.378
Professor, we're all sick
of your upbeat attitude.[ All Agreeing ]

21:26.448 --> 21:30.344
Nonsense. It's just like
in the song I wrote.

21:30.413 --> 21:33.344
♪ We all need
a new angle on life ♪

21:33.413 --> 21:36.000
[ Sighs ]
Bender, you've gotta help us.

21:36.067 --> 21:40.000
I try to get out, but
they keep pullin' me back in!

21:40.067 --> 21:43.654
♪ Wangle a new dangle  on life ♪ [ Bones Cracking, Groaning ]

21:43.723 --> 21:47.517
No, Bender!
The other way!I like him better this way.

21:47.586 --> 21:49.895
I'm sad now.

21:49.964 --> 21:51.895
Eh, it's fine.
